==Personnel==
Joe Strummer and Paul Simonon were the only Clash members that actually appeared on the album.

*[[Joe Strummer]] <U+2013> vocals
*[[Nick Sheppard]] <U+2013> guitar, vocals on "North and South" and "Play to Win"
*[[Mickey Gallagher]] <U+2013> keyboards and synthesizers 
*[[Norman Watt-Roy]] <U+2013> bass
*[[Bernie Rhodes]] <U+2013> drum machine programming
*[[Vince White]] <U+2013> additional guitar on "Do It Now" 
*[[Paul Simonon]] <U+2013> additional bass on "Do It Now"
*[[Pete Howard]] <U+2013> additional drums on "Do It Now"

